      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and honest ride! This car is in solid fair condition, making it the perfect choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle with plenty of life left in it. While it shows some expected signs of its journey so far, it remains a reliable performer that's ready to serve its next owner well. It's a great value for anyone who prioritizes practicality and steady performance over a showroom finish!",
