    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine starts reliably every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a comfortable and confident driving experience. While there are some minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned car that is ready for the road.",
