    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. A buyer can expect a car that looks, feels, and drives like new.",
